Project 1: Player ID Generator

#1. Create a greeting for your program.
#2. Ask the user for the first name.
#3. Ask the user for their year of birth.
#4. Combine their name and year of birth and show them their Player ID
#5. Make sure the input cursor shows on a new line.
#6. How could you include a space inbetween their firstname and yearofbirth in the result?

print("Welcome to the Player ID Generator")
firstname = input("What is your first name?\n")
yearofbirth = input("What is year were you born in?\n")
print("Your Player ID is " + firstname+yearofbirth)

print("Your Player ID is " + firstname+" "+yearofbirth)
